    <h1>{`Configuration In the PagerDuty Web App`}</h1>
    <p>{`##Create an API Key`}</p>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">{`Log in to your PagerDuty account. Navigate to the `}<strong parentName="li">{`Apps & Add-Ons`}</strong>{` :fa-th-large: menu in the upper right and select `}<strong parentName="li">{`API Access`}</strong>{`.`}</li>
