    <h1>{`Verify that ServiceNow and PagerDuty are Communicating`}</h1>
    <p>{`You can verify that PagerDuty and ServiceNow are communicating by creating a new incident in ServiceNow and setting the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Assignment Group`}</strong>{` field to a group that has been mapped to PagerDuty. Below is an incident that was assigned to the Database group which is mapped to PagerDuty. It was then reassigned to the CAB Approval group, as shown in the Activity log.
`}{`[block:image]`}{`
{
"images": [
{
"image": `}{`[
"https://files.readme.io/d0e2433-image3.png",
"image3.png",
910,
